title: Hooked on Phonics
description:
This is the complete set of Hooked on Phonics SRA's from the "Reading Power" Series. Also known as Hooked on Phonics Classic. 

  It is a set of files that I scanned and uploaded. It contains the Answer Sheets, Power builder, and tape dub for the tapes that are included in the set. You will find it all in PDF format, easy to print out. Each booklet is in a separate PDF file.  The tapes are of somewhat poor quality, but I did the absolute best I could. 


  Download and seed. Be sure to use Peerguardian, and a firewall. If the torrent doesn't start downloading immediately, just wait, I have a computer uploading 24/7. 

  Please seed!
